── Disclaimer ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
CEDARS is a research and estimation tool. Its figures are literature-based
estimates, not measured values, and are not medical, clinical, financial, or
regulatory advice. The software is provided "AS IS", without warranty of any
kind (see LICENSE, sections 7–8). Replace defaults with your own measured data
for any reporting of record.

── Privacy ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
CEDARS runs entirely in your browser. It has no backend, collects no personal
data, sets no cookies, and sends nothing you enter off your device.

